task: If I start using Copilot Individual, how much US dollars will it cost per year and what features does it have? Current date is: 2025-01-04.
user_action_and_explanation: click on the 'See plans & pricing' button to view detailed information about the annual cost and features of GitHub Copilot Individual, as it directs to the pricing section which likely contains this information.
observation: GitHub Copilot Individual (Pro) is priced at $10 USD per month. For a year, this would cost $120 USD. It includes unlimited access to GitHub Copilot. The first 30 days are free, and there are special provisions for verified students, teachers, and maintainers of popular open-source projects.

task: If I start using Copilot Individual, how much US dollars will it cost per year and what features does it have? Current date is: 2025-01-04.
observation: The most recent observations indicate that GitHub Copilot Individual (Pro) costs $10 USD per month, totaling $120 USD per year. The plan includes unlimited access to GitHub Copilot, with the first 30 days being free. There are additional benefits for verified students, teachers, and maintainers of popular open-source projects. For the full range of features and a more detailed task history, please refer to the complete task history documentation.
